{"tid":2087811,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日遊行人數，將會影響世界命運","createTime":"2020-06-30T23:32:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-01T09:36:10.000Z","uid":226471,"like":1269,"dislike":41,"uniUserReply":130,"replies":[{"pid":"e389ec1770ea5887de3b9ef4630cc4e292dcf39e","tid":2087811,"uid":226471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T23:32:52.000Z","msg":"呢場係一場世界對抗中共嘅戰爭<br />\n自國安法出爐之後，不單止香港人<br />\n全世界人民嘅自由正受到前所未有嘅威脅<br />\n身為香港人，我地係身處係呢場戰爭嘅最前線<br />\n全世界都會注視今日香港人嘅選擇<br />\n而作出相應嘅對策<br />\n<br />\n今日，有可能成為我地最後的哮聲<br />\n我地今日嘅抉擇，不單止拯救香港<br />\n亦係向全世界發出嘅一張投明狀<br />\n我地絕不屈服<br />\n但願我地係史書上留下嘅<br />\n係流芳百世，唔係遺臭萬年<br />\n<br />\n維園見"},{"pid":"79091c9225133912598a9ecf6859dbadcea4eb51","tid":2087811,"uid":57797,"like":84,"dislike":428,"score":-344,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T23:36:43.000Z","msg":"吹大左啦師兄 世界命運 那來的自信 咁睇得起自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b75d375d05f8aeb9e13b7ca58e742b01334e5a82","tid":2087811,"uid":119485,"like":8,"dislike":23,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T23:37:34.000Z","msg":"吹大左"},{"pid":"89451405f223c4b8afe01319c74022255c712122","tid":2087811,"uid":181549,"like":99,"dislike":3,"score":96,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T23:37:37.000Z","msg":"我獨自去鳩嗚 我謝絕你監管"},{"pid":"8b61b1f3dd1e9e8ffc92f848c52cfe238e5745d7","tid":2087811,"uid":43108,"like":16,"dislike":92,"score":-76,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T23:41:01.000Z","msg":"靠香港人死撚得<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />要返工不了"},{"pid":"3a0252fc37dd6408d4f576a8b5c397be99e57f6f","tid":2087811,"uid":35746,"like":26,"dislike":112,"score":-86,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T23:42:33.000Z","msg":"世界 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />打飛機都唔係咁打呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大把人wfc 香港"},{"pid":"0e7b3ac738cee52ba3d61ae7296b19c91609c2ba","tid":2087811,"uid":35637,"like":24,"dislike":85,"score":-61,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-30T23:44:39.00